{"title":"金字塔 2","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1795","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>  小X来到一个雄奇的金字塔挖宝，但是这是一座被诅咒的金字塔，小X必须马上逃离这里，否则小X就会被埋在金字塔里，但他不希望此行落空。</p>\n<p>  现在小X面前有N+1种财宝，每种财宝都有一个价值。第一种财宝重量为0，第二种财宝重量为1，总之第I种财宝重量为I-1。现在小X希望拿走N+M个物品，但是这M+N个物品总重量不能超过N。小X希望能获得最大的价值。你能帮帮他吗？</p>\n<p> 由于金字塔跟小X一样牛，所以每种财宝无限个。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行两个正整数N，M</p>\n<p>第二行N+1个整数，第I个整数代表了第I种财宝的价值</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个数，表示最大利润。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5 3</p>\n<p>4 7 2 5 -3 6</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>47</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>数据范围：</p>\n<p>10%满足N,M&lt;=10</p>\n<p>40%满足N,M&lt;=100</p>\n<p>100%满足 N,M&lt;=3000 abs(财宝价值)&lt;=1000</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}